		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Geomancy</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">"Geomancer" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Geomancer_(disambiguation)" title="Geomancer (disambiguation)">Geomancer (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">This article is about the African and European divination technique.  For the Chinese art of aesthetics, see <a href="/wiki/Feng_shui" title="Feng shui">Feng shui</a>.</div>
<table class="metadata plainlinks ambox ambox-style" style="">
<tr>
